data.description: Beautiful 3Bed/1Bath brick ranch in Franklin Park! Upgraded home features high vaulted ceilings in the living room, eat-in kitchen with newer high end fridge, upgraded flooring throughout, custom window treatments, new water heater, and laundry area with washer & dryer. Generously-sized 3 bedrooms share a bath that has an updated contemporary vanity. Gorgeous backyard has a large deck that spans the side of the house, a firepit, and a big patio with room for outside dining. Detached 2-car garage also has a second opening facing the backyard as well to allow for even more space while entertaining! Great location right by the Metra.
